LifeVerse DreamVerse ka main area hai.

Isme player ko lagega ki wo ek real, living world me reh raha hai.

Yahan hoga:

- 🏠 House
- 👨‍👩‍👧 Family
- 🐾 Pets
- ❤️ Roleplay
