---

🏡 House System

House Types

LifeVerse me 2 tarah ke ghar honge:

1. Pre-Built Houses

- Main city me ready-made houses honge
- Player unhe kharid sakta hai
- Andar ka furniture customize kar sakta hai

2. Empty Plots

- Player plot kharidega
- Apna ghar khud design karega
- Simple ya creative dono style me ghar bana sakta hai

---

Doorbell System

Har ghar ka doorbell alag sound ka ho sakta hai.

Examples:

- Ding Dong
- Dog Bark
- Cat Meow
- Royal Bell
- Funny Bell
- Sci-Fi Bell
- Piano Bell

---

Mailbox System

Har ghar ke bahar mailbox hoga.

Usme aa sakta hai:

- 💌 Letters
- 🎁 Gifts
- 🎉 Festival Invitations
- 🏆 Rewards
- 📰 DreamVerse Newspaper
- 📢 Announcements

---

👨‍👩‍👧 Family System

Family Types

NPC Family

- Player NPC family create kar sakta hai
- NPCs apni daily life follow karenge
- School, office, shopping, festival sab karenge

Player Family

- Minimum 3 players se family ban sakti hai
- Family name rakh sakte hain
- Family leader hoga
- Members invite / remove kiye ja sakte hain

---

Family Leader

Leader ke paas hoga:

- Invite members
- Remove members
- Family settings change
- House access control

---

🐾 Pet System

Pet Lene ke 2 Tareeke

1. Street Pet

- Roads, parks, beaches me pets milenge
- Player unse dosti karega
- Trust build hoga
- Phir adopt kar sakta hai

2. Pet Shop

- Player pet kharid sakta hai
- Dogs, cats, rabbits, birds, hamsters
- Rare pets secret events se milenge

---

Pet Features

- Pet ka naam rakhna
- Tricks sikhaana
- Khana aur paani dena
- Toys dena
- Bed rakhna
- Pet Hospital
- Training
- Competitions
- Emotional behavior

---

Pet Personality

Har pet alag nature ka hoga:

- Friendly
- Lazy
- Energetic
- Naughty
- Protective
- Funny

Same breed ke do pets bhi alag behave kar sakte hain.

---

Pet Birthday

Har pet ka birthday hoga.

Us din:

- Cake
- Gift
- Party
- Special interaction

---

Pet Friendship

Agar do pets best friends ban jaayein to:

- Wo milne ja sakte hain
- Ek dusre ke ghar ja sakte hain
- Special bond banega

